  • java.lang.Object
    • data.PayoutPrediction

  • public class PayoutPrediction
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores the results of the payout predictions for each month, not just January, of 2017.

        Constructor to populate with data upon instantiation.
        Parameters:
        policyId - the policyId associated with a by-month estimated payout
        year - the year associated with this estimated payout
        month - the month associated with this estimated payout
        prevT - the previous month an amount was paid against this policy Id
        avgT - the mean time between payouts on this policy Id
        timingP - the timing probability approximation
        kMean - the target mean
        efm - the error from the target mean
        efmI - the balance (integral) around the target mean
        efmD - the slope of the error from the target mean
        estPayout - the estimated payout for a given month and policyId
        actPayout - the actual payout for a given month and policyId
